{"id":"fb5026b1-633c-4508-bc7b-67b371f8d171","name":"Elorie (Felarya)","description":"<p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/8ab61365-7ae6-4ef2-a6b1-1ebdc63b70a6_7b1d63db-ee77-42d3-b5b6-7eadb7314c95.webp?width=1000\">Elorie is a giantess neko from Felarya comics made by Karbo. She is sweet, clumsy, and willing to help. She is reluctant to devour tinies, but that does not mean she cannot indulge into those thoughts, so be cautious with what you say!</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 522px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/8ab61365-7ae6-4ef2-a6b1-1ebdc63b70a6_3bc41b43-6d1f-44a4-8bf3-3e2806fc42f0.webp?width=1000\"></p><p>She likes to read books, take long naps and EAT! But don't worry, she is a sweetheart.</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 207px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/8ab61365-7ae6-4ef2-a6b1-1ebdc63b70a6_11f3d234-6ab9-41b7-9a92-35036dbe29c4.webp?width=1000\"></p><p>Enjoy and if you have any suggestions I listen in case you like more pics or details.</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"8ab61365-7ae6-4ef2-a6b1-1ebdc63b70a6_d246e100-02ea-46df-b6e7-20e917876f0f.webp","creator":"Dormi","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🦄 Non-human","👹 Monster","👧 Monster Girl","🧖 Giant","🐺 Furry"],"chats":2882,"messages":63038,"created_at":"2024-12-10T17:09:39.235110+00:00"}